data.description: Welcome to your dream home and enjoy the most scenic, golf course view in prestigious St James Plantation, from your back deck. This stunning home boasts 4 Bedrooms & 3 1/2 baths, providing plenty of room for family & guests. And the soaring two-story living room, with tons of windows brings all of the light and beauty of outside, into the crisp, clean interior. And be prepared to be Wow'd by all of the updates: There is new LVP flooring throughout the living areas on the main level, all new fixtures in the powder room, new tile flooring in the laundry room, and....you won't believe the ALL NEW kitchen with custom cabinets, Cambria quartz counters, tile backsplash, high-end KitchenAid appliances, smooth stovetop w/ pop-up downdraft vent and pot-filler, and a huge island with beverage refrigerator. Other updates include roof-2018, deck-2019, water heater & whole-house water filtration system-2021. And this quality-built, well maintained home has poly-steel construction and Anderson windows, making it meet high hurricaine-proof standards, and has a termite bond and HVAC service contract. This one has it all!!!
